longBusinessSummary: Flitways Technology Inc. provides ground transportation solutions. Its solution provides businesses and private traveler's with access to the booking and scheduling of ground transportation online or by mobile device, as well as provides travelers with access to customizable travel rides through a network of ground travel providers. Flitways Technology Inc. was incorporated in 2012 and is based in West Palm Beach, Florida.
